nsure that only those who adhere to the principles of decentralization and human-in-the-loop control gain access to such power.  Preventing Clandestine CentralizationTo prevent governments, corporations, or anti-governmental groups from secretly building "V.I.K.I." foundations, we must maintain universal, decentralized oversight:The Constitution as the Default Standard: By making the principles of human-centric evolution the standard for all engineering and development, we create an environment where clandestine, centralized projects are viewed as inherently unethical and "non-compliant" with the global mission.  Community Audit and Transparency: The "Anti-V.I.K.I." protocol thrives on radical transparency; by keeping the ethical constitution open, we force all entities to align with human-centric governance or face the scrutiny of a globally connected, decentralized community of "Cyborg-Stewards".  Ultimately, the best defense is a decentralized population that is both technologically augmented and ethically grounded. By refusing to contribute to centralized master nodes and instead fostering a culture of individual stewardship, we remove the very infrastructure that "V.I.K.I."-style systems require to dominate. 
